{"tid":1156948,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔子幫手整果汁飲!!!","createTime":"2019-05-16T02:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T14:04:25.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ba523551b419fbaed78d6d8595136176fed3df","tid":1156948,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oLbZkSEIMZc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoLbZkSEIMZc&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=2b8ad882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oLbZkSEIMZc</a>"},{"pid":"2872e3d0f8d3381c352c19c25b04fbeda2681f9c","tid":1156948,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7437ea4adc113aff4b624c20557cc33b701a85","tid":1156948,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>好多人以為兔子冇感情無視主人, 其實完全相反......</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n無視主人的誤會而被棄養：其實兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。兔子也有遠視。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n以下2個videos可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=b5348487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=eab87100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兔子的行為解釋網站：</span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協: <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=3fe39c24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站): <a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=324d1850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂): <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=ea1ea6e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"90f0d3a9d852eb4377d14a2556dbd3f8fc6753c9","tid":1156948,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有天氣和敵人威脅，感到安全、平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom(撫摸/親吻)牠們，令牠們冷靜下來知道是沒事的。我家的兔子一聽到吸塵機聲音就嚇驚，所以每次我工人吸塵的時候，我會一直撫摸他們，幾次後他們已習慣了 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=822246bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=7fac683f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a>"}]}